&lt;p&gt;Contemporary French cuisine is mastered in Tokyo thanks to Chef Shinobu Namae, who gained experience under icons Michel Bras and Heston Blumenthal, earning him &lt;strong&gt;#95 in&nbsp;the World&amp;#8217;s&nbsp;50 Best Restaurants 2016,&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;#16 Asia&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants 2016&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;one Michelin Star.&lt;/strong&gt; This elegant restaurant in the Nishi Azabu district of Tokyo is sophisticated with polished service by a welcoming staff. Dressy attire- Jacket preferred for gentlemen. Please contact&nbsp;L&rsquo;Effervescence by phone at +81 3-5766-9500 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@leffervescence.jp&quot;&gt;info@leffervescence.jp&lt;/a&gt; or book online through&nbsp;the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.leffervescence.jp/en/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;L&amp;#8217;Effervescence website&nbsp;reservation link&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time and either a cell phone number or a local number in Tokyo where the restaurant can reach you if necessary. Also provide any details if this is a special occasion or if there are allergies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

